<Title>Removable Wing Tip</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Both must be removed. All wires must be capped and stowed and wingtip rear
position lights must be considered inoperative.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>For operations with wing tips removed, the four trailing type dischargers (CDL Item 23-61-01) on each wing just inboard of the removable tip may not be missing</Para>
</Note>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must be dispatched using MEL Item 33-43-01.</Para>
</Note>
